{
  "concept": "vuejs/core#11378: [@vue/compiler-sfc] Failed to resolve index type into finite keys",
  "version": "1.0",
  "created_at": "2026-03-15T04:22:31.021576+00:00",
  "text": "[@vue/compiler-sfc] Failed to resolve index type into finite keys\n\n### Vue version\n\n3.4.27\n\n### Link to minimal reproduction\n\nhttps://play.vuejs.org/#\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\n<script setup lang=\"ts\">\r\ntype TableEmits = (event: \"select\" | \"select-all\" | \"expand-change\" | \"current-change\" | \"selection-change\") => void;\r\ntype ExtractEventNames<T> = T extends (event: infer E, ...args: any[]) => void ? E : never;\r\ntype EventNames = ExtractEventNames<TableEmits>; \r\ntype Emits = {\r\n  [E in EventNames]: any[]; \r\n};\r\nconst emits = defineEmits<Emits>()\r\n</script>\r\n![image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/10129b0a-a466-4575-b9c6-bddfdf2fb32b)\n\n### What is expected?\n\nconst emits: ((evt: \"select\", ...args: any[]) => void) & ((evt: \"select-all\", ...args: any[]) => void) & ((evt: \"expand-change\", ...args: any[]) => void) & ((evt: \"current-change\", ...args: any[]) => void) & ((evt: \"selection-change\", ...args: any[]) => void)\r\n![image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/954ff8aa-3fa6-4ee7-9038-84dee1b3d2c3)\r\n\n\n### What is actually happening?\n\nError: [@vue/compiler-sfc] Failed to resolve index type into finite keys\r\n\r\nsrc/App.vue\r\n1  |  <script setup lang=\"ts\">\r\n2  |  type TableEmits = (event: \"select\" | \"select-all\" | \"expand-change\" | \"current-change\" | \"selection-change\") => void;\r\n   |                                                                                                                        ^\r\n3  |  type ExtractEventNames<T> = T extends (event: infer E, ...args: any[]) => void ? E : never;\r\n   |  ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^\r\n4  |  type EventNames = ExtractEventNames<TableEmits>; \r\n    at bMe.error (https://play.vuejs.org/assets/index-BB5tYPtE.js:185:401)\r\n    at Xu (https://play.vuejs.org/assets/index-BB5tYPtE.js:201:2001)\r\n    at Xu (https://play.vuejs.org/assets/index-BB5tYPtE.js:201:1498)\r\n![image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/3ec270c3-b775-4197-a183-a8df782afe5b)\r\n\r\n    \n\n### System Info\n\n_No response_\n\n### Any additional comments?\n\n_No response_",
